#

Tofu Stir-Fry

25 min
$10
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Asian

Course:

Main

Tags:

QuickHealthyVegetarian

Description

A quick and colorful stir-fry packed with veggies and protein-rich tofu, perfect for a healthy meal!

Ingredients

  • firm tofu: 14 oz
  • broccoli florets: 1 cup
  • bell pepper (sliced): 1
  • carrot (sliced): 1
  • soy sauce: 3 tbsp
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • garlic (minced): 2 cloves
  • ginger (minced): 1 tsp
  • sesame seeds (optional): 1 tbsp
  • green onions (sliced, for garnish): 2
